events.title: Court Order Issued in Maxwell Case
events.description: Judge Alison J. Nathan signs an order in the criminal case United States v. Maxwell (20-cr-330). The order is distributed to counsel and will be entered into the public docket.

keyFacts: The document is a forwarded email containing a court order from Judge Alison J. Nathan.
The order pertains to the criminal case United States v. Maxwell, docket number 20-cr-330.
The order was signed on April 21, 2021, and was to be entered into the public docket the following morning.
The email was sent from Judge Nathan's chambers to counsel, including Jeff Pa liuca and Laura Menninger.
